title Aegis Intelligent Runtime Flow

direction right

Users [icon: users, color: gray] {
  Dispatcher [icon: user, label: "Dispatcher"]
  Supervisor [icon: user-check, label: "Supervisor"]
}

Frontend Layer [icon: monitor, color: blue] {
  React Frontend [icon: react, label: "React + Vite UI"]
  Incident Panel [icon: layout, label: "Incident-Centric View"]
  Live Map UI [icon: map, label: "Live Map"]
}

API and Core Services [icon: server, color: indigo] {
  API Gateway [icon: nginx, label: "Nginx / Gateway"]
  FastAPI Backend [icon: cloud, label: "FastAPI API"]
  Orchestrator Service [icon: workflow, label: "Orchestrator"]
  Emergency Triage Agent [icon: activity, label: "Triage Agent"]
  Dispatch Agent [icon: truck, label: "Dispatch Agent"]
  Response Strategy Agent [icon: target, label: "Strategy Agent"]
  Transport Risk Agent [icon: alert-triangle, label: "Transport Risk Agent"]
  Decision Trace Service [icon: file-text, label: "Decision Trace"]
  Incident Update Service [icon: refresh-cw, label: "Incident Update"]
}

Azure AI Services [icon: azure-resource-groups, color: cyan] {
  Azure OpenAI [icon: azure-openai]
  Azure AI Search [icon: azure-cognitive-search]
  Azure Maps [icon: azure-maps-accounts]
}

Data Layer [icon: database, color: green] {
  Incident Repository [icon: database, label: "Incident Repo"]
  Decision Trace Repository [icon: database, label: "Trace Repo"]
  Patient Repository [icon: database, label: "Patient Repo"]
  Ambulance Repository [icon: database, label: "Ambulance Repo"]
  Provider Repository [icon: database, label: "Provider Repo"]
}

Observability [icon: bar-chart-2, color: purple] {
  Azure Monitor [icon: azure-monitor]
  Application Insights [icon: azure-application-insights]
  Ops Alerts [icon: bell, label: "Ops Alerts"]
}

Dispatcher > React Frontend: request
Supervisor > React Frontend: request
React Frontend > Incident Panel: live updates
React Frontend > Live Map UI: live updates
React Frontend > API Gateway: auth/validate
API Gateway > FastAPI Backend: request
FastAPI Backend > Orchestrator Service: orchestrate

Orchestrator Service > Emergency Triage Agent: triage classify
Orchestrator Service > Dispatch Agent: dispatch decision
Orchestrator Service > Response Strategy Agent: response strategy
Orchestrator Service > Transport Risk Agent: transport risk
Orchestrator Service > Decision Trace Service: decision trace
Orchestrator Service > Incident Update Service: persist updates

Emergency Triage Agent > Azure AI Search: retrieve context
Emergency Triage Agent > Azure OpenAI: reasoning
Dispatch Agent > Azure Maps: route + ETA
Transport Risk Agent > Azure Maps: route + ETA
Response Strategy Agent > Azure OpenAI: reasoning

FastAPI Backend > Incident Repository: read/write
FastAPI Backend > Patient Repository: read/write
FastAPI Backend > Ambulance Repository: read/write
FastAPI Backend > Provider Repository: read/write
Decision Trace Service > Decision Trace Repository: read/write
Incident Update Service > Incident Repository: read/write
Incident Update Service > Orchestrator Service: re-evaluate

FastAPI Backend --> Azure Monitor: telemetry
Orchestrator Service --> Azure Monitor: telemetry
Emergency Triage Agent --> Azure Monitor: telemetry
Dispatch Agent --> Azure Monitor: telemetry
Decision Trace Service --> Azure Monitor: telemetry
Azure Monitor > Application Insights: telemetry
Application Insights > Ops Alerts: telemetry

FastAPI Backend --> React Frontend: live updates

legend {
  [connection: ">", label: "Synchronous call"]
  [connection: "-->", label: "Async event / telemetry"]
}
